'''Church''' is a [[Roman Catholic]] [[List of churches in the Roman Catholic Archdiocese of New York#Churches in Dutchess County|parish church]] under the authority of the [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of New York]], located in [[Pleasant Valley, New York|Pleasant Valley]], [[Dutchess County, New York|Dutchess County]], [[New York City]]. It was established as a parish in 1903; formerly staffed by the [[Society of Jesus|Jesuits]].

